+## 🤖 6. AI MAINTAINABILITY
+
+### 6.1 Good: Clean and Organized Code
+
+**Status:** ✅ **GOOD**
+
+- Clear separation of concerns (lib.rs, schema.rs, collection.rs, types.rs)
+- Well-organized macros (parser, builder, models, relationships, factory_observer)
